List.Title: Views Information
List.Content:
**1.Overrides**

Overrides view shows all overrides **since last upload minus 1 day**.

**2.Rules**

Rules view shows **all** overridden rules.

**3.Monitors**

Monitors view shows **all** overridden monitors.

**4.Data Amount**

Received Data view shows the data received for monitors and rules over a period of time. In addition the amount of data records.

**5.Queries**

A collection of useful queries.

Tile.Query: (Type=EffMonitor_CL AND TimeGenerated>NOW-1DAY AND Overridden_b=true) OR (Type=EffRule_CL AND TimeGenerated>NOW-1DAY  AND Overridden_b=true) | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s

List.Query: (Type=EffMonitor_CL AND TimeGenerated>NOW-1DAY AND Overridden_b=true) OR (Type=EffRule_CL AND TimeGenerated>NOW-1DAY  AND Overridden_b=true) | sort DisplayName_s DESC | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s,Type_s

Donut.Query: * Type=EffRule_CL Overridden_b=true | measure countdistinct(ManagementPack_s) by DisplayName_s

List.Query: * Type=EffRule_CL Overridden_b=true | sort DisplayName_s DESC | measure countdistinct(ManagementPack_s) by DisplayName_s, ManagementPack_s

Donut.Query: * Type=EffMonitor_CL Overridden_b=true | measure countdistinct(ManagementPack_s) by DisplayName_s

List.Query: * Type=EffMonitor_CL Overridden_b=true | sort DisplayName_s DESC | measure countdistinct(ManagementPack_s) by DisplayName_s, ManagementPack_s

LineChart.Query: Type=EffMonitor_CL OR Type=EffRule_CL | measure count() by Type | display linechart

List.Query: Type=EffMonitor_CL OR Type=EffRule_CL | measure count() by Type

queries.query: Type=EffMonitor_CL TargetObject_s="XA74.CMXDEMO.LAN" Overridden_b = true | measure countdistinct(TargetClass_s) by TargetObject_s
Type=EffMonitor_CL Overridden_b = true | measure countdistinct(TargetClass_s) by TargetObject_s
Type=EffMonitor_CL Overridden_b=true | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s
Type=EffRule_CL Overridden_b=true | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s
Type=EffMonitor_CL Overridden_b = true | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by TargetClass_s
(Type=EffMonitor_CL AND Overridden_b=true) OR (Type=EffRule_CL AND Overridden_b=true) | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s,Type_s
queries.displayName: All overrides per rule or monitor

queries.query: Type=EffMonitor_CL  OR Type=EffRule_CL  | measure countdistinct(ManagementPack_s) by ManagementPack_s
Type=EffRule_CL Overridden_b=false OR Overridden_b=true  | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s, Overridden_b, TargetClass_s | sort DisplayName_s ASC
Type=EffMonitor_CL Overridden_b=false OR Overridden_b=true  | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by DisplayName_s, Overridden_b, TargetClass_s | sort DisplayName_s ASC

Donut.Query: (Type=EffRule_CL AND Overridden_b=true) OR  (Type=EffMonitor_CL AND Overridden_b=true) | measure countdistinct(DisplayName_s) by Type_s

DataFlowVerification.Message: Please use PowerShell Module 'SendEffectiveConfiguration' to populate the view. Module is available on PowerShell Gallery.
